	r Lake Community Center\n\nContact: Bitter Lake Community Center\n\nContac
	t Phone: 2066847524\n\nAudience: Adults\,All\,Children\,Family\,Se nior\,S
	pecial Needs\n\nPre-Register: No\n\nCost: Free\n\nLink: https://anc.apm.ac
	tivecommunities.com/seattle/activity/search/detail/79824?onlineSiteId=0&fr
	om\\_original\\_cui=true\n\nJoin your friends and neighbors for Bitter Lak
	e Community Center's Annual Pancake Breakfast! Bring the whole family and 
	enjoy breakfast favorites like scrambled eggs\, sausage\, coffee\, and of 
	course all-you-can-eat pancakes! Proceeds from t his event will help provi
	de scholarships to those in need throughout the year. Volunteers are neede
	d for this event\; please call 206-684-7524 for additional info.\n\nFrom S
